      out.write("\n");
      out.write("        <p style=\"color: #000B58;\">B.Tech stands for Bachelor of Technology. It is an undergraduate degree focused on technical and engineering disciplines.\n");
      out.write("            B.Tech programs are highly popular in countries like India, as well as some parts of Europe and Asia. The degree\n");
      out.write("             is considered equivalent to the Bachelor of Engineering (BE) in most countries, although some institutions may differentiate \n");
